		<td><b>right and left combos</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It seems that very few emulators allow user to press left and right (or up and down) simultaneously.
<br />
<br />So far i have found only one emulator that allows this; Famtasia.
<br />FCE Ultra and Nintendulator (i think) do not allow L+R combos.
<br />
<br />Is there any other emulators (except Famtasia), that allows L+R combos?
<br />- Sepi

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
