	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There is a modified version of FCEU, used by the <a href="http://bisqwit.iki.fi/nesvideos/" class="postlink">tool-assisted speedrun scene</a>, which allows L+R.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

