	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Nintendulator 0.955 Beta allows L+R (and U+D) as a global setting for all controllers - the option is located right at the bottom of the main 'Input Configuration' dialog.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


